graph TD
    A[Start] --> B{Is Data Valid?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Process Data]
    B -->|No| D[Return Error]
    C --> E[Save to Database]
    E --> F{Save Successful?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Return Success]
    F -->|No| H[Rollback]
    H --> D
    D --> I[End]
    G --> I
    
